    <updated>2026-02-26T00:54:00+09:00</updated>
    <content type="html">        &lt;body&gt;
            &lt;img src="https://image-cdn.tver.jp/images/content/thumbnail/series/xlarge/srpyus1d8b.jpg"&gt;

            &lt;hr&gt;

            &lt;div&gt;🎞️ こちら予備自衛英雄補?!
                &lt;a href="https://tver.jp/series/srpyus1d8b" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer"&gt;🔗&lt;/a&gt;
